<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lien expiré - KTC Invoice Pro</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f3f4f6; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .container { background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,.1); padding: 3rem; text-align: center; max-width: 480px; margin: 1rem; }
        .icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .icon svg { width: 40px; height: 40px; color: #ef4444; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
        p { color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: .75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: background .2s; }
        .btn:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Lien expiré ou invalide</h1>
        <p>Ce lien de partage n'est plus valide. Il a peut-être expiré ou a été révoqué par l'expéditeur.</p>
        <p>Veuillez contacter la personne qui vous a envoyé ce lien pour obtenir un nouveau lien de consultation.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
